00:02:11.193 --> 00:02:22.500
The Samsung Galaxy Note Edge screen made me feel uncomfortable a lot, especially when I was making hasty moves.

00:02:22.663 --> 00:02:28.050
I could not get used to it at all even until the last day of shipping it back to Samsung. 

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:35.200
Let's take a look at the technical spefications of the Note Edge.

00:02:35.300 --> 00:02:46.300
