00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:28.700
The However, I felt like it didn't last as much as I wanted, since it could not last for more than a day.

00:03:28.812 --> 00:03:47.100
Undoubtedly, the highlight of the smartphone is its famous "Edge' Screen. Most people think it is an extension of the screen but that's false. It is an autonomous screen that helps the user with his/her daily tasks. 

00:03:47.289 --> 00:04:01.300
The Edge screen has display a lot of information, like notifications from Facebook, which can be customized by the user.

00:04:01.428 --> 00:04:09.080
Moreover, a lot of applications like the camera app take advantage of the Edge screen which leaves more space to the main screen.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:16.200
Last but not least, Samsung added the ability to have a personalized design and information stream.

00:04:16.300 --> 00:04:34.200
As much as I'd love to be impressed by the Edge screen, I believe it is a gimmick rather than something useful. I also found myself touching it accidentally a lot of times. 

00:04:34.336 --> 00:04:54.000
If someone can disregard the Edge screen, the Samsung Galaxy Note Edge is an impressive phone. The smartphones comes with Android 4.4.4 pre-installed and brings with it the improved Samsung Android "skin".

00:04:54.106 --> 00:04:58.400
Regarding the Samsung Android skin, I feel like everything has been re-organized neatly and that more control has been given to the user. 

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:10.000
The Samsung Galaxy Note Edge is an extremely fast phone and it will certainly disappoint you. The multi-tasking capabilities made my experience with the Note Edge a lot better.

00:05:10.205 --> 00:05:24.700
The display of the Samsung Galaxy Note Edge is probably the best one in the high-end smartphone market right now. From its extremely vibrant colors and brightness to the excellent black color levels, the screen of the Note Edge will render you speechless.

00:05:24.887 --> 00:05:59.400
The 3.7 front camera can capture 440p video at 30fps while the 16MP rear camera can capture 4K video at 30fps and 1080p video at 60fps. The rear camera's performance at low light situations was amazing. 

